comments.author: minairia3
comments.body: The market is having beautiful recovery days and finally only because of the battle of the 2 biggest market giants that the market once again dropped below 20k $. It is true that nothing is predictable in crypto, everything happens so suddenly. There have been some reports that SBF is looking to retaliate against CZ by selling BNB, if that really happens we will see a more bloody market.
